{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_52_02",
  "title": "kana 2話 雪山に埋めるかんな",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなそれぞれ、旅行を楽しんでいるみたいだし\n俺も観光にでも行ってみようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone seems to be enjoying their trip\nshall I go sightseeing too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "普段は旅行なんて行けないしな……ん？\nあれは……kanaさん？　凄い形相でこっちに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't usually get to go on trips… huh?\nIs that… kana-san? She came this way looking cold…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3647327582,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9166.6667143,
          "startTime": 17.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2000003338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……おい{user}！　寒い！！\nあんたのせいで、kana死にそうなんですけど！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey {user}! Cold!!\nBecause of you‚ kana going to die!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そりゃ北海道ですからね\nどうしたんですか、写真撮りに行ってたはずじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ because it's Hokkaido\nWhat happened? Weren't you supposed to go take pictures…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1333336671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "は？　言われなくてもちゃんと行って来たっつーの！\nkanaが映えスポット逃す訳ないじゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I went there properly without you telling meー!\nThere's no way kana would miss any filming spot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "人気の観光スポットとか、移動中にリスト作って\nちゃんと回って来たんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made a list of famous spots‚ while on the move\nand I went around to all of them",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6333336671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらさあ、途中で雪は降ってくるしスマホ対応\n手袋は誤タッチ連発するし……ホンット最悪！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ suddenly started snowing‚ and my smartphone-compatible\ngloves were spamming touch errors… It's really the worst!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……それは災難でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ ahaha… That was a accident",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1000003338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.1000003338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも旅行行きたいとか頼んでないのに他のやつらと\nお徳用パックみたいにまとめて連れて来られてさぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't ask to go on a trip in the first place‚ but\nyou brought me along with the others like a value pack",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.9666670005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "それなのにこんな寒い思いして\nkanaってばかわいそう過ぎない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And yet‚ I'm suffering in this cold\nIsn't kana too pitiful?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当にお疲れ様でした\n夜は旅館でゆっくり温まっていただけると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ you really worked hard\nI hope you can relax and warm up at the inn tonight…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.3000003338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "は？　何言ってんの？　これからまた撮影に行くんだよ\n夜景なんて鉄板ネタをスルーするとか、ポンコツかよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What are you talking about? I'm going out to shoot again now\nSkip a classic subject like night views? Are you an idiot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}は撮影係な\nkanaのこと可愛く撮らないと許さないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user} is in charge of filming\nkana won't forgive you if you don't take a cute picture",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.4000003338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました。パッと行ってパッと暖かい\n旅館に帰って来ましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay. Let's go quickly and\ncome back to the inn",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.4333336671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "は？　そんなテキトーで許されると思ってんの？\nkanaのことバカにしてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa? Do you think you'll be forgiven for something so half-hearted?\nAre you treating kana like a fool?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません！　しっかりkanaさんを\n撮影させていただきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry! I'll make sure to\nto good film kana-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1133508165,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3586.6491835000006,
          "startTime": 112.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkadeck-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.2166670005
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkadeck-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.2166670005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……どうせ話盛ってるだろうと思ったけど\n北海道の夜景も、悪くはないんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… why they're exaggerating‚ but\nHokkaido's night view isn't so bad",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、向こうのコンビニでキタキツネがゴミ漁ってる\nたくましいな、こっちの野生生物……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ there's a red fox rummaging through the trash at that convenience store over there\nThese wild animals are tough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkadeck-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.0333336671
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkadeck-00-night",
      "startTime": 136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "ま、これならkanaを引き立てる背景にはなるでしょ\nはい、これkanaのスマホ。こっちは携帯用のレフ板",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ this will make a good background to highlight kana\nHere‚ kana's smartphone. And this is a portable reflector",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "さっさと撮ってよ、いい写真撮れたらすぐ帰るんだから\nあ、でもブサかったら雪山に埋めるかんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make it quick‚ we'll go back once we get a good shot\nAh‚ but if it's ugly‚ I'll going to bury you in the snowy mountains",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkadeck-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.6666670005
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkadeck-00-night",
      "startTime": 152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、それじゃ、撮りますよ\nさすがkanaさん、笑顔もポーズも完璧です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…O-Okay‚ I'll take the picture\nVery good kana-san‚ smile and pose are perfect",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.666332799974,
          "startTime": 152.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4999.999666199983,
          "startTime": 154.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前でしょ？　kanaを誰だと思ってんの。ほら\n次はもっと上から！　レパートリーなさ過ぎでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ right? Who do you think kana is? Hey\nNext‚ from a higher angle! Repertoire is too small",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
